---
layout: base.njk
title: Work With Me — Fred Deichler
description: "1:1 coaching, team workshops, speaking engagements, and transformation consulting. Help your team achieve predictable delivery through evidence-based practices."
---

<main id="main" class="container">
  <h1>Work With Me</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); max-width: 800px;">
    Whether you need coaching, workshops, speaking, or transformation consulting, I bring 13+ years of experience 
    helping 50+ teams achieve predictable delivery through evidence-based practices.
  </p>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="grid four">
    <div class="card fade-in">
      <h2>1:1 Agile Coaching</h2>
      <p>Personalized coaching for Scrum Masters, Product Owners, Agile leaders, and teams looking to level up their practice.</p>
      <ul class="tight">
        <li>Individual coaching sessions tailored to your challenges</li>
        <li>Evidence-based techniques for improving team effectiveness</li>
        <li>Practical strategies you can implement immediately</li>
        <li>Ongoing support and accountability</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card fade-in">
      <h2>Team Workshops</h2>
      <p>Custom workshops designed to address your team's specific challenges and drive measurable improvements.</p>
      <ul class="tight">
        <li>Predictable Delivery with Flow Metrics & Monte Carlo</li>
        <li>AI Integration in Agile Teams</li>
        <li>Evidence-Based Management (EBM)</li>
        <li>Advanced Scrum & Kanban Practices</li>
        <li>Team Working Agreements & Collaboration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card fade-in">
      <h2>Speaking Engagements</h2>
      <p>Engaging keynotes, breakout sessions, and workshops for your conference, company event, or team offsite.</p>
      <ul class="tight">
        <li>40+ international talks across 15+ conferences</li>
        <li>Topics: Delivery, AI, Coaching, Transformation</li>
        <li>Formats: Keynote, Workshop, Breakout Session</li>
        <li>Typical duration: 45-90 minutes</li>
        <li>Virtual or in-person options available</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/speaking/" class="btn outline" style="margin-top: var(--space-md); display: inline-flex;">View Talks</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card fade-in">
      <h2>Transformation Consulting</h2>
      <p>Enterprise Agile adoption strategy and implementation support to help your organization scale effectively.</p>
      <ul class="tight">
        <li>Agile transformation strategy & roadmapping</li>
        <li>Scaling frameworks (SAFe, LeSS, Scrum@Scale)</li>
        <li>Flow metrics implementation & training</li>
        <li>Release management & predictability improvement</li>
        <li>Kanban Center of Excellence setup</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="card fade-in" style="background: var(--gradient-subtle); border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);">
    <h2>How We'll Work Together</h2>
    <div class="grid four" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: var(--orange);">1. Discovery</h3>
        <p>We'll start with a conversation to understand your challenges, goals, and current state. This helps me tailor the engagement to your specific needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: var(--orange);">2. Proposal</h3>
        <p>I'll provide a clear proposal outlining the approach, timeline, deliverables, and investment required to achieve your goals.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: var(--orange);">3. Engagement</h3>
        <p>We'll work together through coaching sessions, workshops, or consulting engagements using evidence-based practices and proven frameworks.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: var(--orange);">4. Outcomes</h3>
        <p>You'll see measurable improvements in team predictability, delivery speed, and overall effectiveness—with metrics to prove it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="card fade-in">
    <h2>What People Say</h2>
    <div id="services-testimonials" class="grid two">
      {% for q in testimonials %}
        <div class="quote">
          <p style="margin:0 0 .5rem 0">"{{ q.quote }}"</p>
          <small style="color:var(--text-secondary)">{{ q.author | default('Attendee') }}{% if q.event %} — {{ q.event }}{% endif %}</small>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing & CTA -->
  <section class="card fade-in" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);">
      Pricing varies based on the scope, duration, and format of the engagement. Let's discuss your specific needs 
      and I'll provide a custom proposal.
    </p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn primary">Get In Touch</a>
      <a href="/about/" class="btn outline">Learn More About Me</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section style="text-align: center;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">Proven Results</h2>
    <div class="grid three">
      <div class="card fade-in">
        <h3 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--orange); margin: 0;">55% → 88%</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">Predictability Improvement</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card fade-in">
        <h3 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--orange); margin: 0;">50+</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">Teams Coached</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card fade-in">
        <h3 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--orange); margin: 0;">Zero</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">Missed Critical Dates (2022-2023)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
